title: Star Trek TMP Warp Re-Edit (2010) - deLimited Productions Fanedi
description:
Summary: All three versions of Star Trek: The Motion Picture (TMP) are brought to bear in this fanedit, but with entirely new shots, cutting and reorganization throughout. The result is an exciting, high-quality re-vision of the first Star Trek feature film, 30 years later.

For more information about this work, visit the official project page: <a href="
http://digital-fanedits.com/database/86-star-trek-the-motion-picture-warp-re-edit" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://digital-fanedits.com/database/86-star-trek-the-motion-picture-warp-re-edit</a>

 Star Trek TMP Warp Re-Edit (2010) - H.264 MKV

         deLimited Productions fanedit
-----------------------------------------------

This reference-quality MKV release includes chapter metadata
and an English subtitle stream.

The video is presented in a PAL-DVD frame to avoid problems
with players and displays that do not readily support ana-
morphic 720x432 data. Note also that the high-quality nature
of this encode can produce bitrate spikes of 10,000kbps.

Video: 720x576 anamorphic widescreen (H.264/AVC, CQ13, 3RF)
Audio: Dolby Digital 5.1 Surround (AC3, 448kbps)

Note. Also available in PAL DVD-5 format.
